channel.title: [HELP]" Server Already in use" problem [HELP]
channel.description: Everytime I run my server it says "Server is already in use." I don't know what's wrong. When I try to check if my port is open it says "Port 43594 could not be checked. Please close any applications that may be using this port and try again." WILL SOMEONE HELP PLEASE :confused:

its most likely utorrent if your using it. just close utorrent from taskbar, turn server on, then turn on utorrent.
